    • Constructor Detail

      • HttpRequestTask

        public HttpRequestTask(java.lang.Class answer,
                       HttpRequest executor,
                       java.lang.String url)
        Creates a request task. The request must then be started to with execute.
        A GET request is used by default, use setMethod to change this.
        The Body is empty by default. Use setJSONBody to define the body.
        Verify if addAPIAuthentication is needed
        Use setType if 'executor' (httpRequest) can receive different answers and/or implements different behaviours
        Parameters:
        answer - answer type expected, must e deserializable
        executor - the instance that implements the HttpRequest. Only needed to run request on background (can be null).
        url - request destination
